languages.en: How can I take a screenshot of our conversation and upload it as a receipt for the top-up?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh ambil screenshot perbualan kami dan muat naik sebagai resit untuk top-up?

detailed.en: To take a screenshot of our conversation, you can follow these steps: 1. Open the chat screen. 2. Press the 'Power' and 'Volume Down' buttons simultaneously (for most phones). 3. The screenshot will be saved in your phone's gallery. Make sure to include all necessary information in the screenshot. If you have any issues taking the screenshot, let me know, and I'll assist you!
detailed.ms: Untuk ambil screenshot perbualan kami, anda boleh ikut langkah-langkah ini: 1. Buka skrin sembang. 2. Tekan butang 'Power' dan 'Volume Down' serentak (untuk kebanyakan telefon). 3. Screenshot akan disimpan dalam galeri telefon anda. Pastikan untuk menyertakan semua maklumat yang diperlukan dalam screenshot. Jika anda mempunyai sebarang masalah mengambil screenshot, beritahu saya, dan saya akan bantu!

question.text: What should I do if my top-up hasn't been processed yet after sending the receipt?
variations: Why hasn't my top-up been credited yet?
What is the processing time for my top-up?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up hasn't been processed yet after sending the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya belum diproses selepas menghantar resit?

detailed.en: If the receipt has been sent and the top-up still hasn't been credited, it may be in the processing stage. Please be patient, as it usually takes the designated time to process. If there are any other issues or questions, feel free to ask!
detailed.ms: Jika resit sudah dihantar dan top-up masih belum masuk, mungkin ia sedang dalam proses. Sabar sekejap ya, biasanya ia akan diproses dalam masa yang ditetapkan. Jika ada masalah lain atau soalan, jangan segan untuk tanya!

question.text: What are the requirements for making a refund to a bank account that has a different name from the registered name?

languages.en: What are the requirements for making a refund to a bank account that has a different name from the registered name?
languages.ms: Apakah syarat untuk membuat pengembalian wang kepada akaun bank yang mempunyai nama berbeza daripada nama yang didaftarkan?

detailed.en: To process a refund, please provide the bank account number and the name of the account holder. The name on the deposit must match the registered name. In this case, you need to provide the account number for Tan Chor Keat, and the refund will be made to that account.
detailed.ms: Untuk memproses pengembalian wang, sila berikan nombor akaun bank dan nama pemilik akaun. Nama pada deposit mesti sepadan dengan nama yang didaftarkan. Dalam kes ini, anda perlu memberikan nombor akaun untuk Tan Chor Keat, dan pengembalian wang akan dibuat ke akaun tersebut.

question.text: How can I obtain a receipt from an ATM after making a deposit?
variations: Saya nak cari print resit dlm

languages.en: How can I obtain a receipt from an ATM after making a deposit?
languages.ms: Saya nak cari print resit dlm

detailed.en: If the ATM does not produce a receipt after a deposit, please provide transaction details such as the transfer method (ATM Card/Cash Deposit/Online), time of transfer, bank name, amount deposited, and sender's name. This information will help us verify your transaction. You can also contact support via live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika mesin ATM tidak menghasilkan resit selepas deposit, sila berikan butiran transaksi seperti kaedah pemindahan (Kad ATM/Deposit Tunai/Online), waktu pemindahan, nama bank, jumlah yang dideposit, dan nama pengirim. Maklumat ini akan membantu kami mengesahkan transaksi anda. Anda juga boleh menghubungi sokongan melalui live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: I have transferred RM10, can I top up another RM10 to make it RM20?
variations: Kalau sy trnsfer rm10 lg smuanya topup rm20 ka bos
Tadi sudah topup rm10

languages.en: I have transferred RM10, can I top up another RM10 to make it RM20?
languages.ms: Kalau sy trnsfer rm10 lg smuanya topup rm20 ka bos

detailed.en: If you have already topped up RM10 earlier, you only need to transfer another RM10 to reach a total of RM20. Please ensure you upload both receipts in the live chat (not on the top-up page) so we can process it for you. Wait for 3-10 minutes for confirmation. If you have any other questions, just let us know!
detailed.ms: Jika anda sudah top-up RM10 tadi, anda hanya perlu transfer RM10 lagi untuk mencapai jumlah RM20. Pastikan anda upload kedua-dua resit ke dalam live chat (bukan di halaman top-up) supaya kami boleh proses untuk anda. Tunggu 3-10 minit untuk pengesahan. Jika ada apa-apa soalan lain, beritahu saja, boss!

question.text: Saya telah melakukan transfer yang salah dan ingin tahu bagaimana untuk mendapatkan kembali wang saya.
variations: Bos sy salah tranfer tak cukup rm10
Refund kt no akaun saya boleh ke?

languages.en: I have made an incorrect transfer and would like to know how to get my money back.
languages.ms: Saya telah melakukan transfer yang salah dan ingin tahu bagaimana untuk mendapatkan kembali wang saya.

detailed.en: For a refund, we can only process it to the account number registered with the account owner's name (FKA GROUP RESOURCES). If you want a refund to your own account number, that cannot be done. Please provide the correct account number and account owner's name for us to process.
detailed.ms: Untuk refund, kami hanya boleh memproses kepada nombor akaun yang didaftarkan dengan nama pemilik akaun (FKA GROUP RESOURCES). Jika anda ingin refund ke nombor akaun anda sendiri, itu tidak dapat dilakukan. Sila berikan nombor akaun dan nama pemilik akaun yang betul untuk kami proses.

question.text: What should I do if I encounter issues logging into my wallet after a top-up?

languages.en: What should I do if I encounter issues logging into my wallet after a top-up?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya menghadapi masalah log masuk ke dalam dompet saya selepas top-up?

detailed.en: If you encounter issues logging into your wallet after a top-up, ensure that your username and password are correct, and check your internet connection. If you have any other questions or issues, feel free to ask!
detailed.ms: Jika anda menghadapi masalah log masuk ke dalam dompet anda selepas top-up, pastikan nama pengguna dan kata laluan anda betul, dan semak sambungan internet anda. Jika anda mempunyai sebarang soalan atau masalah lain, jangan ragu untuk bertanya!

question.text: How do I top up my account using the JOKER app and what should I do if I encounter issues?

languages.en: How do I top up my account using the JOKER app and what should I do if I encounter issues?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh topup akaun saya menggunakan aplikasi JOKER dan apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya menghadapi masalah?

detailed.en: To top up, you only need to upload the receipt in the Topup section of the JOKER app. Do not send it here (live chat) because the system will only check receipts sent on the top-up page. After uploading, wait for 3â€“10 minutes for the system to process. If there are any issues, you can send a screenshot of the transaction and select the correct bank, then contact us again.
detailed.ms: Untuk topup, resit hanya perlu upload di bahagian Topup dalam app JOKER sahaja ya. Jangan hantar di sini (livechat) sebab sistem hanya akan semak resit yang dihantar di halaman topup. Lepas upload, tunggu 3â€“10 minit untuk sistem proses. Kalau ada masalah, boleh hantar screenshot transaksi + pilih bank yang betul, dan roger kami semula ya boss.

question.text: Why is there a delay, boss? Can you clarify what context you are referring to, such as top-up, winnings, or withdrawals?
variations: Why is it slow, boss?
What is causing the delay, boss?

languages.en: Why is there a delay, boss? Can you clarify what context you are referring to, such as top-up, winnings, or withdrawals?
languages.ms: Kenapa lambat ya boss? Boleh tahu lambat dalam konteks apa ya, seperti top-up, kemenangan, atau pengeluaran?

detailed.en: I understand, boss! Can you tell me what context the delay is in? It could be regarding top-up, winnings, or withdrawals. Then I can assist you more accurately.
detailed.ms: Faham, boss! Boleh tahu lambat dalam konteks apa ya? Mungkin top-up, kemenangan, atau pengeluaran? Nanti saya boleh bantu lebih tepat.

question.text: What should I do if my Fast Payment (eWallet) transaction does not go through after 10 minutes?

languages.en: What should I do if my Fast Payment (eWallet) transaction does not go through after 10 minutes?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika transaksi Fast Payment (eWallet) saya tidak berjaya selepas 10 minit?

detailed.en: If you are using Fast Payment (eWallet), please wait for 10 minutes as the system is processing. If the transaction has not gone through after 10 minutes, you can contact us again for further checks. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika anda menggunakan Fast Payment (eWallet), sila tunggu selama 10 minit kerana sistem sedang memproses. Jika transaksi tidak berjaya selepas 10 minit, anda boleh menghubungi kami semula untuk semakan lanjut. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: I made a mistake in the amount I wrote, how can I correct it?
variations: I wrote the wrong amount, what should I do?
How do I fix the amount I submitted?

languages.en: I made a mistake in the amount I wrote, how can I correct it?
languages.ms: Saya telah membuat kesilapan dalam jumlah yang saya tulis, bagaimana saya boleh membetulkannya?

detailed.en: Please re-upload the document and ensure that the amount is written as RM 20.
detailed.ms: Sila muat naik semula dokumen dan pastikan jumlah ditulis sebagai RM 20.

question.text: I have not received my points for the game I played. Can you help me with this issue?
variations: tdi tpp x masok pon point

languages.en: I have not received my points for the game I played. Can you help me with this issue?
languages.ms: tdi tpp x masok pon point

detailed.en: If you are using Fast Payment (eWallet), please wait for 10 minutes as the system is processing. If the points still do not appear after 10 minutes, you can contact us again for further checks. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Kalau guna Fast Payment (eWallet), mohon tunggu dalam 10 minit ya, sistem sedang proses. Kalau masih belum masuk selepas 10 minit, boss boleh roger kami semula untuk semakan lanjut. Terima kasih atas kesabaran boss!

question.text: What are the time limits for topping up my account?
variations: Top ip limit sampai jam berapa bos
What time can I top up my account?

languages.en: What are the time limits for topping up my account?
languages.ms: Top ip limit sampai jam berapa bos

detailed.en: For topping up, there is no specific time limit, but the process usually completes within 3-10 minutes. If you use Fast Payment (FPX), it is faster and automatic within 1-3 minutes. If you have any issues or further questions, feel free to ask!
detailed.ms: Untuk top-up, tiada had waktu tertentu, tetapi biasanya proses top-up akan selesai dalam 3-10 minit. Jika anda menggunakan Fast Payment (FPX), ia lebih cepat dan automatik dalam 1-3 minit. Jika ada masalah atau pertanyaan lain, jangan ragu untuk tanya ya!

question.text: What should I do after uploading the receipt?

languages.en: What should I do after uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: The receipt has been successfully uploaded. Please wait a moment for the system to process it. Do not upload the same receipt again as it may slow down the system. Thank you for your patience and cooperation!
detailed.ms: Resit telah berjaya dimuat naik. Sila tunggu sebentar untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jangan muat naik resit yang sama lagi kerana ia mungkin melambatkan sistem. Terima kasih atas kesabaran dan kerjasama anda!

question.text: What should I do if my withdrawal has not been approved yet?
variations: ape belum approve lgi

languages.en: What should I do if my withdrawal has not been approved yet?
languages.ms: ape belum approve lgi

detailed.en: If your withdrawal has not been approved yet, don't worry! The process usually takes 5-30 minutes to be processed. If you still haven't received it after 30 minutes, please reply here and provide the transaction details for immediate checking. I will help check for you!
detailed.ms: Kalau pengeluaran belum diluluskan lagi, jangan risau! Biasanya proses ambil masa 5-30 minit untuk diproses. Kalau masih belum diterima selepas 30 minit, boleh balas sini dan berikan butiran transaksi untuk semakan segera. Saya akan bantu check untuk boss!

question.text: Why hasn't my banking transaction been credited yet?
variations: dah banking Belum masuk lagi

languages.en: Why hasn't my banking transaction been credited yet?
languages.ms: dah banking Belum masuk lagi

detailed.en: If the funds have not been credited after the expected time, please send your transaction details via live chat so we can check it immediately. Additionally, ensure that the receipt has been uploaded to the top-up page in the app. After uploading, wait 1-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. If it still hasn't been credited after 10 minutes, you can send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate verification.
detailed.ms: Jika wang masih belum masuk selepas jangka masa yang dijangka, sila hantarkan butiran transaksi anda melalui live chat supaya kami dapat semak dengan segera. Selain itu, pastikan resit sudah diupload ke halaman topup dalam app. Lepas upload, tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem sahkan transaksi. Kalau lebih 10 minit masih belum masuk, boleh hantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera.

question.text: Why is my top-up pending for so long?
variations: lama nya pending topup

languages.en: Why is my top-up pending for so long?
languages.ms: Mengapa top-up saya tertangguh begitu lama?

detailed.en: I understand, sometimes there are delays in processing top-ups. Please ensure you have uploaded the transaction receipt in the top-up section of the app. Wait for 1-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. If it is still not credited after 10 minutes, you can send a screenshot via live chat for immediate assistance. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Saya faham, kadang-kadang ada kelewatan dalam pemprosesan top-up. Pastikan anda telah memuat naik resit transaksi dalam bahagian top-up aplikasi. Tunggu dalam 1-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan transaksi. Jika masih belum dikreditkan selepas 10 minit, anda boleh menghantar tangkapan skrin melalui sembang langsung untuk bantuan segera. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: What should I do if my bank transaction receipt is unclear and has been rejected?
variations: What to do if the receipt is blurry?
How can I resolve issues with my bank transaction receipt?

languages.en: What should I do if my bank transaction receipt is unclear and has been rejected?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika resit transaksi bank saya tidak jelas dan ditolak?

detailed.en: If the receipt you sent is the same as the previous one, the system may reject it. Ensure that the uploaded receipt is different for a smoother process. If you have any other questions or need further assistance, just let me know!
detailed.ms: Jika resit yang kamu hantar sama dengan yang sebelum ini, sistem mungkin akan menolak. Pastikan resit yang diupload adalah berbeza untuk proses yang lebih lancar. Jika ada apa-apa lagi yang perlu dibantu atau jika kamu ada soalan lain, beritahu saja, ya!

question.text: Kawan saya sudah menunggu lebih dari 10 minit dan masih belum dapat akses, apa yang perlu dilakukan?
variations: Kawan saya sudah berapa minggu tunggu dan masih belum dapat buka.
Apa yang perlu dilakukan jika kawan saya tidak dapat akses setelah menunggu lama?

languages.ms: Kawan saya sudah menunggu lebih dari 10 minit dan masih belum dapat akses, apa yang perlu dilakukan?

detailed.en: If your friend has been waiting for more than 10 minutes and still cannot access, there may be a system issue. Please ask them to resend the receipt or transaction information to us. We will assist in checking and ensuring everything runs smoothly. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika kawan anda sudah menunggu lebih dari 10 minit dan masih belum dapat akses, mungkin ada masalah dengan sistem. Sila minta dia untuk menghantar semula resit atau maklumat transaksi kepada kami. Kami akan bantu semak dan pastikan semuanya berjalan lancar. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: Bagaimana cara untuk melakukan top-up?
variations: macam mana nak top up?
apa langkah-langkah untuk top up?

languages.ms: macam mana nak top up?

detailed.ms:
Salam boss! Kalau nak topup, boleh ikut langkah ini:

ğŸ“Œ Min Topup:
âœ… ATM/Transfer (DuitNow/Instant Transfer) â€“ Min RM10
âœ… Fast Payment (FPX) â€“ Min RM50 (lebih cepat & automatik)

ğŸ“Œ Cara Topup:
1ï¸âƒ£ Pergi ke halaman topup dalam app.
2ï¸âƒ£ Pilih kaedah topup (ATM/Transfer atau Fast Payment).
3ï¸âƒ£ Masukkan jumlah topup & upload resit (jika guna ATM/Transfer).
4ï¸âƒ£ Tekan "Submit" & tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem sahkan transaksi.

ğŸ“Œ Kalau lebih 10 minit masih belum masuk, boleh hantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera.

Kalau ada pertanyaan lain, boleh roger kami di live chat ya boss! ğŸ˜ŠğŸ™

question.text: What should I do if my credit balance suddenly goes to zero after topping up?
variations: Why is my credit balance empty?
What happens if my credit doesn't show up after a top-up?

languages.en: What should I do if my credit balance suddenly goes to zero after topping up?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika baki kredit saya tiba-tiba kosong selepas top-up?

detailed.en: If you have topped up RM50 but the credit hasn't appeared, it usually takes 3 to 10 minutes to process. Please check the transaction in the app first. If it has been more than 10 minutes and you still haven't received it, please send the complete transaction receipt via live chat for further inspection. We will assist you as soon as possible!
detailed.ms: Jika kamu sudah top-up RM50 tetapi kredit belum masuk, biasanya ia mengambil masa 3 hingga 10 minit untuk diproses. Sila semak transaksi dalam aplikasi terlebih dahulu. Jika sudah lebih 10 minit dan masih belum diterima, sila hantar resit transaksi lengkap melalui live chat untuk pemeriksaan lanjut. Kami akan bantu secepat mungkin!

question.text: What should I do after uploading the receipt?
variations: What happens after I upload the receipt?
Is there anything else I need to do after uploading the receipt?

languages.en: What should I do after uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: The receipt has been successfully uploaded. Please wait a moment for the system to process it. Do not upload the same receipt again as it may slow down the system. Thank you for your patience and cooperation!
detailed.ms: Resit telah berjaya dimuat naik. Sila tunggu sebentar untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jangan muat naik resit yang sama lagi kerana ia mungkin melambatkan sistem. Terima kasih atas kesabaran dan kerjasama anda!

question.text: Can you help me check the status of my transaction or game?
variations: boleh tolong check x
ada kne ka

languages.en: Can you help me check the status of my transaction or game?
languages.ms: Boleh tolong semak status transaksi atau permainan saya?

detailed.en: If you have topped up using Touch 'n Go (TNG) for RM60 but it hasn't reflected yet, it usually takes 1-3 minutes to process. If it has been more than 3 minutes and it still hasn't appeared, please check the transaction in the TNG app first. If there is still no update, send us the FPX transaction receipt via live chat for further verification. We will assist in processing it as quickly as possible!
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah top-up menggunakan Touch 'n Go (TNG) sebanyak RM60 tetapi belum masuk, biasanya ia mengambil masa 1-3 minit untuk diproses. Jika sudah lebih dari 3 minit dan masih belum masuk, sila semak transaksi dalam aplikasi TNG terlebih dahulu. Jika masih tiada, hantarkan resit transaksi FPX kepada kami melalui live chat untuk pemeriksaan lanjut. Kami akan bantu proses secepat mungkin!

question.text: What does the term 'kena' mean in this context? Is it related to a number, a game issue, or something else?
variations: What does 'kena' mean?
Is 'kena' referring to a number or a game problem?

languages.en: What does the term 'kena' mean in this context? Is it related to a number, a game issue, or something else?
languages.ms: Apa maksud istilah 'kena' dalam konteks ini? Adakah ia berkaitan dengan nombor, masalah permainan, atau sesuatu yang lain?

detailed.en: Hi boss ğŸ˜Š If you could provide a bit more detail about what you mean by 'kena', I can help check it out for you. Is it related to a number, a game issue, or something else?
detailed.ms: Hai bos ğŸ˜Š Jika anda boleh memberikan sedikit lebih banyak butiran tentang apa yang anda maksudkan dengan 'kena', saya boleh membantu menyemaknya untuk anda. Adakah ia berkaitan dengan nombor, masalah permainan, atau sesuatu yang lain?

question.text: What should I include in the recipient reference when making an online transfer?
variations: What details are needed for the recipient reference?
How do I fill in the recipient reference for online transfers?

languages.en: What should I include in the recipient reference when making an online transfer?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya masukkan dalam rujukan penerima semasa membuat pemindahan dalam talian?

detailed.en: When making an online transfer, please ensure to fill in your JOKER ID in the 'Recipient Reference' field along with other payment details. This is crucial for us to verify the receipt quickly.
detailed.ms: Semasa membuat pemindahan dalam talian, sila pastikan untuk mengisi ID JOKER anda dalam ruangan 'Rujukan Penerima' bersama dengan butiran pembayaran lain. Ini sangat penting untuk kami mengesahkan resit dengan cepat.

question.text: I have withdrawn money, but it hasn't appeared in my bank account yet. What should I do?

languages.en: I have withdrawn money, but it hasn't appeared in my bank account yet. What should I do?
languages.ms: Saya telah mengeluarkan duit, tetapi ia belum muncul dalam akaun bank saya. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?

detailed.en: If the withdrawal has been more than 30 minutes and the money has not yet appeared, please check the transaction status in the app. If it still hasn't appeared, you can send us the transaction details via live chat for immediate checking. We will help ensure everything goes smoothly for you. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika pengeluaran sudah lebih dari 30 minit tetapi belum masuk, sila semak status transaksi dalam aplikasi ya. Jika masih tiada, boleh hantar butiran transaksi kepada kami melalui sembang langsung untuk semakan segera. Kami akan bantu pastikan semuanya berjalan lancar untuk anda. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: What should I do if my credit has not been received after topping up?
variations: What to do if the credit hasn't arrived?
How long does it take for the credit to show up?

languages.en: What should I do if my credit has not been received after topping up?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kredit saya belum diterima selepas top up?

detailed.en: If you have topped up and the credit has not been received, please wait for 3-10 minutes for confirmation. If the funds still do not appear, send the receipt via live chat for further assistance. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the credit is still not in, please send a screenshot of the transaction receipt for immediate checking.
detailed.ms: Jika anda sudah top up dan kredit belum diterima, sila tunggu dalam 3-10 minit untuk pengesahan. Jika dana masih belum masuk, hantar resit melalui live chat untuk bantuan lanjut. Jika sudah lebih 10 minit dan kredit masih belum masuk, sila hantar tangkapan layar resit transaksi untuk semakan segera.

question.text: Do I need to enter a reference number when transferring money using an ATM machine?
variations: Is a reference number required for ATM transfers?
Do I have to input a reference number for transfers at the ATM?

languages.en: Do I need to enter a reference number when transferring money using an ATM machine?
languages.ms: Kalau nk transfer guna mesin atm kena letak no rujukan ke

detailed.en: When using an ATM for transfers, it is not necessary to enter a reference number. Just make sure to take a clear picture of the ATM receipt after the transfer and upload it to the top-up section in the app. Then, wait for 3 to 10 minutes for the system to process automatically.
detailed.ms: Kalau guna mesin ATM, tak perlu letak nombor rujukan pun tak apa. Boss cuma pastikan lepas transfer, ambil gambar resit ATM yang jelas dan upload ke bahagian topup dalam app. Lepas tu tunggu 3â€“10 minit saja, sistem akan proses automatik.

question.text: Can you confirm if my account is functioning correctly?
variations: Betol tak boss acc nie
Dah masuk ke boss
bet 4d boss

languages.en: Can you confirm if my account is functioning correctly?
languages.ms: Boleh tahu boss maksudkan tentang akaun yang mana satu?

detailed.en: Please upload your bank slip through (WALLET -> TOPUP). The process will take about 3-5 minutes. Thank you, boss!
detailed.ms: Sila uplaod slip bankin anda melalui (WALLET -> TOPUP) proses ambil masa dalam 3-5min, tq boss, mantapâ¤ï¸â¤ï¸

question.text: What should I do after uploading the receipt?

languages.en: What should I do after uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: The receipt has been successfully uploaded. Please wait a moment for the system to process it. Do not upload the same receipt again as it may slow down the system. Thank you for your patience and cooperation!

question.text: What do the abbreviations BT, BH, and RV mean in the context of betting?
variations: BT BH RV apa mksud dia
Sama mcm box jg ke?

languages.en: What do the abbreviations BT, BH, and RV mean in the context of betting?
languages.ms: BT BH RV apa mksud dia

detailed.en: In the context of 4D betting, the abbreviations mean the following: RV (Round Return â€“ Reverse Balik) refers to a number that is completely reversed (e.g., 1234 becomes 4321). BH (Pao Kepala â€“ First Digit Fixed) means the first digit remains the same while the others can change (e.g., 1223 can become 1232 or 1322). BT (Pao Ekor â€“ Last Digit Fixed) indicates that the last digit does not change while the others can be rearranged (e.g., 1223 can become 2123 or 2213). Additionally, IBOX is similar to BOX but with a fixed price of RM1, and the payout is divided according to the number of combinations. BOX is a bet that includes all possible combinations (the arrangement of digits can change).
detailed.ms: Dalam konteks pertaruhan 4D, singkatan ini bermaksud: RV (Round Return â€“ Reverse Balik) merujuk kepada nombor yang dibalik sepenuhnya (contohnya, 1234 menjadi 4321). BH (Pao Kepala â€“ Nombor Pertama Tak Bergerak) bermaksud digit pertama kekal sama manakala yang lain boleh berubah (contohnya, 1223 boleh jadi 1232 atau 1322). BT (Pao Ekor â€“ Nombor Akhir Tak Bergerak) menunjukkan bahawa digit terakhir tidak berubah manakala yang lain boleh disusun semula (contohnya, 1223 boleh jadi 2123 atau 2213). Selain itu, IBOX adalah sama seperti BOX tetapi dengan harga tetap RM1, dan pembayaran dibahagikan mengikut bilangan kombinasi. BOX adalah pertaruhan yang merangkumi semua kemungkinan kombinasi (susunan digit boleh berubah).

question.text: What are the rules and procedures for making a deposit and withdrawal in this gaming platform?
variations: What do I need to know about deposits and withdrawals?
Can you explain the deposit and withdrawal process?
What are the requirements for transactions?

languages.en: What are the rules and procedures for making a deposit and withdrawal in this gaming platform?
languages.ms: Apakah peraturan dan prosedur untuk membuat deposit dan pengeluaran di platform permainan ini?

detailed.en:
1. **Top-up**: Minimum RM50 for fast transfer. Ensure to upload the receipt with JOKER ID within 1-3 minutes.

2. **Betting**: Ensure to place bets before the specified deadline. For example, for GD Lotto, bets must be placed before 6:59 PM.

3. **Problem Resolution**: If there are issues with top-up or betting, check the bank account and transaction records. If necessary, contact customer support.

For any specific questions about the game or other rules, feel free to ask! I'm here to help!
detailed.ms:

question.text: Why hasn't my withdrawal from the game been credited to my account yet?
variations: Why is my withdrawal taking so long?
What could be causing the delay in my withdrawal?

languages.en: Why hasn't my withdrawal from the game been credited to my account yet?
languages.ms: Kenapa pengeluaran saya belum masuk ke akaun?

detailed.en: There are several reasons why a withdrawal may be delayed: 1. **Bank processing delays**: Sometimes banks take time to process transactions. 2. **Non-compliance with requirements**: There may be conditions that have not been met, such as wagering requirements. 3. **Maintenance issues**: Occasionally, system maintenance can cause delays. If you have waited a long time and it still hasn't been credited, it's best to provide transaction details to customer support for further checks. Don't worry, we will help resolve this!
detailed.ms: Ada beberapa sebab kenapa pengeluaran mungkin lambat: 1. **Kelewatan pemprosesan bank**: Kadang-kadang bank mengambil masa untuk memproses transaksi. 2. **Ketidakpatuhan syarat**: Mungkin ada syarat yang belum dipenuhi, seperti keperluan pertaruhan. 3. **Isu penyelenggaraan**: Kadang-kadang ada penyelenggaraan sistem yang boleh menyebabkan kelewatan. Kalau dah tunggu lama dan masih tak masuk, lebih baik bagi butiran transaksi kepada sokongan pelanggan untuk semakan lanjut. Jangan risau, kita akan bantu selesaikan!

detailed.en: If you forgot to enter the referral code during registration, it usually cannot be added after the account has been created. However, you can try contacting customer support to see if there is another way to resolve this issue.
